>\n<br />\n你會相信這學校的在校生，<br />\n敢犯下需要十個防暴圍毆制服的滔天大罪嗎？<br />\n銀行劫匪？恐怖分子？無差別殺人狂？<br />\n<br />\n什麼叫非法集結？<br />\n「週末晚上，在自己住的區，和幾個同學在街上行」<br />\n如果這叫非法集結，<br />\n咁我肯肯肯定看倌你都試過非法集結十次以上吧？<br />\n<br />\n就當學生真的是非法集結，程序上是衝過去無須答辯直接圍毆打穿頭打斷骨嗎？<br />\n<br />\n乖乖校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec96f0e16b3f406d5a2f2b0e67d8de7a92973cd","tid":1554177,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:21:38.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5734571489da5ff47cda73de48ae243dccfb20db","tid":1554177,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bad132a09a0b7befed24b12d2c992adf9251874","tid":1554177,"uid":281977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:23:38.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13470e7eb3fcc33fea6a1ba4f9987835c1e45ea7","tid":1554177,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5defe9e6b4328a4f4d1f8bcef66efa5f899eafe","tid":1554177,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"唔好講推 將所有核彈列明黎推post 不能被習慣任何一樣 屌你老母黑警死全家！<br />\n<br />\n1. 射頭+射眼<br />\n2. 721無起訴 警黑合作<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者 記得所有違法野都係啲臥底做<br />\n4. 無理由無差別不合理濫捕 拘捕後繼續用武力<br />\n5. 室內開槍漠視人命 <br />\n6. 過份使用武力 打人同虐待人<br />\n7. 冇委任證+遮面 唔可以習慣左冇委任證<br />\n8. 過期催淚彈 揚左後繼續射 特登刻走日子<br />\n9. 警黑勾結 警藍勾結<br />\n10. 過度濫權 個個開工前食興奮劑<br />\n11. 光明正大講大話 +誣蔑市民+陷害市民<br />\n12. 公然拆證物+陷害<br />\n13. 新屋嶺強姦及歐打<br />\n14. 無視任何法律及指引 警權過大<br />\n15. 近距離、無警告下開槍<br />\n16. 831事件 歐打市民 趕走記者 唔俾救護入 草菅人命 殺完人事但扔條屍出黎 再自己定義無可疑<br />\n17. 被影到不只幾次喺醫院/黑房歐打市民<br />\n18. 非禮女手足<br />\n19. 喺多個狗鐵濫捕 虐打市民 漠視人權<br />\n<br />\n佢地搞到香港咁樣 人人都生意差冇工開佢地仲計ot幾萬蚊準時出糧一定唔驚，諗計斷班撚樣既飯碗<br />\n香港人唔再需要唔保護市民既警察！！唔想再出糧俾一啲開槍打我 用棍扑我既人<br />\n<br />\n有手足想加減借用隨便<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n清算警隊 血債血償"},{"pid":"f776f44f3bbfb50dfe540f97cfb4390b8481b2cb","tid":1554177,"uid":196538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12386c46db2885c4875906d987b37a98cb9b9b5","tid":1554177,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ea1d7c8622cbe2b36244b89fa5e030104ebd2e","tid":1554177,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563c2530b6cb173176e28ea02b1e0bb92268a074","tid":1554177,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:43:59.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d8ba220d6e72732aed80322481236966d05740fb","tid":1554177,"uid":275024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357bee24b3e74f95fc530d335cc9112b0b5961a8","tid":1554177,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:44:34.000Z","msg":"叻仔黎<br />\n依間係全大埔最難入果間"},{"pid":"55f718172297e866